Class Node

java.lang.Object
Node
public class Node extends Object
The Node class handles how each Node is constructed. This method adds Postcodes, Suburbs, Adjacent Edges and Amenities and handles the subsequent removal methods
Author:
Jayath Gunawardena created on 19/05/2023
